{"tid":844763,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"金童獎候選名單出爐 麥巴比有望破天荒冧莊","createTime":"2018-10-02T06:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T13:16:56.000Z","uid":4661,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"517af7ca342ff9e2d56ec4cd3ebe0ae384bd56fb","tid":844763,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:22:33.000Z","msg":"本年度歐洲金童獎於周一公佈新一輪的40人候選名單，入圍球員包括法國國腳基利安麥巴比，這位世界盃冠軍成員有望成為史上首位兩度奪得此獎的年青球員。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲金童獎由利大利體育報章突圖體育由2003年開始舉辦，每年選出一位表現最出色的21歲或以下球星，過往曾經贏得金童獎的包括雲達華治、朗尼、美斯、法比加斯、阿古路和保羅普巴等，這班金童後來都成為了世界球壇的頂級球星。<br />\n<br />\n除了去年得主麥巴比有份入選外，今屆獲得提名進入40入名單之中有四位英超球員入選，包括利物浦後衛阿歷山大阿諾特、曼城中場菲爾科頓、愛華頓中場湯姆戴維斯以及今季轉投曼聯的葡萄牙後衛達洛治。<br />\n<br />\n至於其他聯賽方面同樣有不少熟悉的名字入圍，包括皇家馬德里的雲尼斯奧斯祖利亞、多蒙特後衛阿舒拉夫和中場基斯甸普列錫、巴黎聖日耳門前鋒添莫菲韋亞和羅馬前鋒祖斯甸古華特兩位名將之後。<br />\n<br />\nThe 40 nominees<br />\n<br />\nTrent Alexander-Arnold (Liverpool)<br />\nKelvin Amian (Toulouse)<br />\nHoussem Aouar (Lyon)<br />\nMusa Barrow (Atalanta)<br />\nJustin Bijlow (Feyenoord)<br />\nJosip Brekalo (Wolfsburg)<br />\nPatrick Cutrone (AC Milan)<br />\nDani Olmo (Dinamo Zagreb)<br />\nTom Davies (Everton)<br />\nMatthijs De Ligt (Ajax)<br />\nMoussa Diaby (PSG)<br />\nDiogo Dalot (Manchester United)<br />\nMoussa Djenepo (Standard Liege)<br />\nRitsu Doan (Groningen)<br />\nEder Militao (Porto)<br />\nOdsonne Edouard (Celtic)<br />\nEvander (Midtjylland)<br />\nPhil Foden (Manchester City)<br />\nAchraf Hakimi (Borussia Dortmund)<br />\nAmadou Haidara (Red Bull Salzburg)<br />\nJoao Felix (Benfica)<br />\nJota (Benfica)<br />\nJovane Cabral (Sporting Lisbon)<br />\nDejan Joveljic (Red Star Belgrade)<br />\nBoubacar Kamara (Marseille)<br />\nMoise Kean (Juventus)<br />\nJules Keita (Dijon)<br />\nJustin Kluivert (Roma)<br />\nAlban Lafont (Fiorentina)<br />\nManu Garcia (Toulouse)<br />\nKylian Mbappe (PSG)<br />\nPietro Pellegri (Monaco)<br />\nChristian Pulisic (Borussia Dortmund)<br />\nMarcelo Saracchi (RB Leipzig)<br />\nIsmaila Sarr (Rennes)<br />\nDayot Upamecano (RB Leipzig)<br />\nVinicius Junior (Real Madrid)<br />\nMoussa Wague (Barcelona)<br />\nTimothy Weah (PSG)<br />\nNicolo Zaniolo (Roma)"},{"pid":"8550e91dcdbb45d8a5591db2441e796665e54995","tid":844763,"uid":52571,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"對比起其他高成十個level<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d866bc924f6134da9233ab655813a70b3ab50ad","tid":844763,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"淨係捧世界盃都屌打晒所有人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54557a4059ec6248cd303868f77432d53b787722","tid":844763,"uid":54025,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，金童獎可以拎到22歲，包皮應該可以破紀錄4奪金童獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b84e89181f05de629529360dcd2a7332f96ffe","tid":844763,"uid":5649,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"54557a4059ec6248cd303868f77432d53b787722","tid":844763,"uid":54025,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，金童獎可以拎到22歲，包皮應該可以破紀錄4奪金童獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:27:30.000Z","msg":"除非Jesus 帶巴西拎世界盃，唔係都好難有人贏到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa82246222d3a3cb2fbbee4b6ce9aa1809756f1","tid":844763,"uid":52571,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"93b84e89181f05de629529360dcd2a7332f96ffe","tid":844763,"uid":5649,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"54557a4059ec6248cd303868f77432d53b787722","tid":844763,"uid":54025,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，金童獎可以拎到22歲，包皮應該可以破紀錄4奪金童獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T